data.title: The Icelandic Phallological Museum
data.meta_description: The world's only genuine penis museum, The Icelandic Phallological Museum, is dedicated to collecting, studying and presenting actual phalluses and all things phallic.
data.text:
F= FHL = Full-Gildir Heiðurslimir - Donors of genuine, phallic pieces

A= AHL = All-Gildir Heiðurslimir - Donors of extra things, a work of art, etc. and other true

G= GGL = Gildir Gervilimir - Pseudomember, having shown special interest in the works and development of the Institute
